title: AFC Projected Starters
itunes:title: AFC Projected Starters
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Conor Orr, & Gregg Rosenthal – recap all the latest news from around the NFL including Bills GM Brandon Beane declaring an open competition at quarterback, and Chiefs QB Patrick Mahomes being robbed at gunpoint in Texas. Then, the heroes go around the AFC projecting who they think will be starters come September.
